{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Council Tax bands"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/council-tax-bands.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/council-tax-bands"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"176","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Find out the Council Tax band for a property in England, Scotland or Wales by looking up the property's postcode online","updated_at":"2012-10-09T18:03:27+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Find out the Council Tax band for your home by looking up your property online.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If your home is in England or Wales, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.voa.gov.uk/cti/InitS.asp?lcn=0\" title=\"Search for your Council Tax band\">search for your property by postcode.</a> </p>\n\n<p>You can search for homes in Scotland on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.saa.gov.uk/\" title=\"Scottish Assessor\">Scottish Assessor</a> website.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>In England and Scotland, valuation bands are based on levels of value on 1 April 1991, not what a property is worth today. In Wales, valuation bands are based on levels of value on 1 April 2003.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Council Tax","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/housing%2Fcouncil-tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes bands, arrears, appeals and Council Tax Benefit","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=housing%2Fcouncil-tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/housing/council-tax"},"parent":{"title":"Housing","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/housing.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Your legal obligations and rights when renting, buying or owning a home, plus information about Council Tax, what to do if you're homeless and where to get help if you have a housing dispute.","type":"section"}